David was found in Hanover Township, Washington County, in the southwestern corner of Pennsylvania, reported CBS Pittsburgh.

West Virginia authorities have been looking for the fugitive since he was accused two weeks ago of molesting a co-worker's young daughter.

David is a convicted sex offender who also was wanted for not registering under Megan's Law for a 1999 molestation case.

