At around 2.30pm Tuesday, some 30 law enforcement officials from various agencies converged on David’s hideout and arrested him without incident.

Speaking to WTOV9, the young victim’s mother said her boyfriend had met David at work a few months back and befriended him.

About three weeks ago, the 64-year-old moved his RV closer to his new friends’ property in Follansbee, West Virginia.

